For Each CommonChatbots.GXChatMessage Order (GXChatMessageDate) Where GXChatUserId = &Id AND GXChatMessageInstance = &Instance &Meta = GXChatMessageMeta exit EndFor
If not &Meta.IsEmpty() &ContextProperties.FromJson(&Meta) &Action = &contextProperties.Get(ChatbotContextElements.GXAction) &Clean = &contextProperties.Get(ChatbotContextElements.GXClean) If &Action = ChatbotContextElements.GXNoAction OR &Clean = ChatbotContextElements.GXTrue &Meta.SetEmpty() EndIf Else &Meta = ChatbotContextElements.GXEmptyContext Endif
parm(in:&Id, in:&Instance, out:&Meta);

&Add = true For Each CommonChatbots.GXChatUser Where GXChatUserId = &User AND GXChatUserDevice = &ClientId &Add = false endfor
if &Add = true &ChatUser.GXChatUserId = &User &ChatUser.GXChatUserDevice = &ClientId &ChatUser.Save() commit endif
&ChatMessage.GXChatMessageId = Guid.NewGuid() &ChatMessage.GXChatUserId = &User &ChatMessage.GXChatMessageMessage = &Message &ChatMessage.GXChatMessageType = &Type &MessageDateTime = DateTime.Now() &ChatMessage.GXChatMessageDate = &MessageDateTime &ChatMessage.GXChatMessageImage = &Image &ChatMessage.GXChatMessageMeta = &Meta &ChatMessage.GXChatMessageRepeat = &Repeat &ChatMessage.GXChatUserDevice = &ClientId &ChatMessage.GXChatMessageInstance = &Instance &ChatMessage.Save() commit
parm(in:&User, in:&Type, in:&Message, in:&Image, in:&Meta, &Repeat, in:&ClientId, in:&Instance);
&UserId.FromString('6AB18499-CA51-4C36-AC15-4F6735FB09E4')
parm(out:&UserId);

For Each CommonChatbots.GXChatMessage where GXChatMessageId = &ChatMessageId &ContextString = GXChatMessageMeta &AnalyzeResponse.FromJson(&ContextString) &WebComponentLink = &AnalyzeResponse.Context.GXComponentWeb EndFor
parm(in:&ChatMessageId, out:&WebComponentLink);

for each GXChatMessage order (GXChatMessageDate) where GXChatUserId = &UserId AND GXChatMessageInstance = &Instance &Context = GXChatMessageMeta exit when none &Cache = Cache.GetCache(&Instance) if &Cache.Contains(&UserId.ToString()) &Context = &Cache.Get(&UserId.ToString()) endif endfor
parm(in:&Instance, in:&UserId, out:&Context);

for each GXChatMessage order (GXChatMessageDate) where GXChatUserId = &UserId AND GXChatMessageInstance = &Instance GXChatMessageMeta = &Context exit when none &Cache = Cache.GetCache(&Instance) &Cache.Set(&UserId.ToString(), &Context) endfor
parm(in:&Instance, in:&UserId, in:&Context);
parm(inout:&Messages, out:&ShowErrorsInUI);

&UserId = GetUserId()
&MessageType = ChatbotMessageTypes.User if not &Image.IsEmpty() &MessageType = ChatbotMessageTypes.UserImage endif
&PreviousContext = GetChatMeta(&UserId, &Instance) NewMessage(&UserId, &MessageType, &Message, &Image, &PreviousContext, !"", &ClientId, &Instance)
&AnalyzeResponse.FromJson(&PreviousContext) &AnalyzeResponse.Context.GXUserId = &UserId.ToString()
NotifyClients(&UserId, &ClientId, ChatbotNotificationTypes.ChatbotMessage, !"", false)
Chatbot.Message.SendMessage(&Instance, &Message, &Image, &AnalyzeResponse, &Messages)
if &Messages.Count = 0 &Meta = &AnalyzeResponse.ToJson() Do Case Case not &AnalyzeResponse.Context.GXQuery.IsEmpty() &MessageType = ChatbotMessageTypes.Query Case not &AnalyzeResponse.Context.GXComponentWeb.IsEmpty() &MessageType = ChatbotMessageTypes.ResponsePanel if &ChatbotPlatform = ChatbotPlatform.SmartDevices &ShowMessage = !"Show" endif Otherwise &MessageType = ChatbotMessageTypes.Response EndCase for &GXResponse in &AnalyzeResponse.GXResponse if not &GXResponse.GXResponseImage.IsEmpty() &MessageType = ChatbotMessageTypes.ResponseImage endif NewMessage(&UserId, &MessageType, &GXResponse.GXOutput, &GXResponse.GXResponseImage, &Meta, &ShowMessage, &ClientId, &Instance) NotifyClients(&UserId, &ClientId, ChatbotNotificationTypes.ChatbotMessage, !"", false) endfor else NotifyClients(&UserId, &ClientId, ChatbotNotificationTypes.ChatbotError, &Messages.ToJson(), false) endif
parm(in:&Instance, in:&ChatbotPlatform, in:&Message, in:&Image, in:&ClientId);

&NotificationInfo.Id = &ChatbotNotificationType &NotificationInfo.Message = &NotificationMessage for each GXChatUser where GXChatUserId = &UserId where not (&IsFromClient AND GXChatUserDevice = &SourceClient) &Socket.NotifyClient(GXChatUserDevice, &NotificationInfo) endfor
parm(in:&UserId, in:&SourceClient, in:&ChatbotNotificationType, in:&NotificationMessage, in:&IsFromClient);

For Each CommonChatbots.GXChatMessage where GXChatMessageId = &ChatMessageId &Meta = GXChatMessageMeta EndFor
&Context.FromJson(&Meta) &Context.FromJson(&Context.Get(ChatbotContextElements.GXContext)) &GXCallPanelSD = &Context.Get(ChatbotContextElements.GXCallPanelSD) &GXComponentSD = &Context.Get(ChatbotContextElements.GXComponentSD)
Do Case Case not &GXCallPanelSD.IsEmpty() &SDComponentLink = &GXCallPanelSD &IsCallPanel = true Case not &GXComponentSD.IsEmpty() &SDComponentLink = &GXComponentSD &IsCallPanel = false Otherwise &IsCallPanel = false EndCase
parm(in:&ChatMessageId, out:&SDComponentLink, out:&IsCallPanel);

&UserId = GetUserIdByDevice(&ClientId) GetChatMeta(&UserId, &Instance, &Meta)
&AnalyzeResponse.FromJson(&Meta) &AnalyzeResponse.Context.GXUserId = &UserId.ToString()
NewMessage(&UserId, ChatbotMessageTypes.User, &Message, &Image, &Meta, !"", &ClientId, &Instance)
Chatbot.Message.SendMessage(&Instance, &Message, &Image, &AnalyzeResponse, &Messages)
if &Messages.Count > 0 Log.Debug(Format(!"Chatbot output: %1", &Messages.ToJson())) else for &GXResponse in &AnalyzeResponse.GXResponse NewMessage(&UserId, ChatbotMessageTypes.Response, &GXResponse.GXOutput, !"", &AnalyzeResponse.ToJson(), !"", &ClientId, &Instance) endfor endif
parm(in:&Message, in:&Image, in:&ClientId, in:&Instance, out:&AnalyzeResponse);
for each GXChatUser where GXChatUserDevice = &ClientId &UserId = GXChatUserId exit when none &UserId = Guid.NewGuid() new GXChatUserId = &UserId GXChatUserDevice = &ClientId endnew endfor
parm(in:&ClientId, out:&UserId);
for &CustomContextProperty in &AnalyzeResponse.CustomContext if &CustomContextProperty.Key = &Key &Value = &CustomContextProperty.Value return endif endfor
parm(in:&AnalyzeResponse, in:&Key, out:&Value);
parm(in:&Instance);

Event Start WebComponentTable.Class = themeclass:CFCollapseWebComponent &WebClient = &WebNotification.ClientId &UserId = GetUserId() Endevent
Event 'Send' if not &Send.IsEmpty() Do 'SendMessage' endif Endevent
Event GridSent.Load WebComponentTable.Class = themeclass:CFWebComponent GXChatMessageDate.Class = themeclass:ReadonlyCFDate GXChatMessageImage.Class = themeclass:CFResponseMessageImageHidden Do Case case GXChatMessageType = ChatbotMessageTypes.User WebComponentTable.Class = themeclass:CFCollapseWebComponent GridMessagesTable.Class = themeclass:CFSendMessageTable GXChatMessageMessage.Class = themeclass:ReadonlyCFSendMessage case GXChatMessageType = ChatbotMessageTypes.Response or GXChatMessageType = ChatbotMessageTypes.ResponseImage WebComponentTable.Class = themeclass:CFCollapseWebComponent GridMessagesTable.Class = themeclass:CFResponseMessageTable GXChatMessageMessage.Class = themeclass:ReadonlyCFResponseMessage if GXChatMessageType = ChatbotMessageTypes.ResponseImage GXChatMessageImage.Class = themeclass:CFResponseMessageImage endif case GXChatMessageType = ChatbotMessageTypes.ResponsePanel &WebComponentLink = GetWebComponentById(GXChatMessageId) WebComponent.Object = CreateFromUrl(&WebComponentLink) WebComponentTable.Class = themeclass:CFWebComponent GridMessagesTable.Class = themeclass:CFResponseMessageTableComponent GXChatMessageMessage.Class = themeclass:CFResponseMessage otherwise WebComponentTable.Class = themeclass:CFCollapseWebComponent endcase Endevent
Event OnMessage(&NotificationInfo) Do Case Case &NotificationInfo.Id = ChatbotNotificationTypes.ChatbotMessage GridSent.Refresh() Case &NotificationInfo.Id = ChatbotNotificationTypes.ChatbotError &Messages.FromJson(&NotificationInfo.Message) &ShowErrorsInUI = ErrorHandling(&Messages) if &ShowErrorsInUI for &Message in &Messages msg(&Message.Description) endfor endif EndCase EndEvent
Event GlobalEvents.EnumeratedEvent(&Send) Do 'SendMessage' Endevent
Event GlobalEvents.BotEvent(&Send) Do 'SendMessage' Endevent
Sub 'SendMessage' //Send Message CommonChatbots.SendMessage.Submit("", &Instance, ChatbotPlatform.Web, &Send, "", &WebClient) &Send.SetEmpty() endsub
